bug.short_desc: Add a carrousel to the qooxdoo start page

long_desc.thetext:
We currently show only the showcase on qooxdoo's front page. It would be nice to have a carrousel like e.g. http://www.omnigroup.com/ have for their apps.
Before we start with that, Feedback is welcome and we have to decide about the final look.

Created attachment 985 First prototype
Here ist the first prototype Gabriel did some time ago. This should be the base for further development.
